Package: LexFreq
Title: Compute Lexical Frequency measures for text.
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Bodong", "Chen", , "bodong.chen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package compute Lexical Frequency measures for text. Measures include: Lexical frequency measures defined in Lexical Frequency Profile defined by Laufer (1994) and P_Lex defined by Meara & Bell (2001). These measures can be used to assess complexity of writing in terms of used vocabulary.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.2)
License: GPL 2.0
LazyData: true
